    Um, not till the end of the book, dear, that's kind of the point. It's called "Flowers In The Attic" not "Flowers On The Street"; the book about them <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Um, not till the end of the book, dear, that's kind of the point. It's called "Flowers In The Attic" not "Flowers On The Street"; the book about them AFTER the attic is "Petals On The Wind".<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
