<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I would read Flowers, Petals On the Wind (revenge), and Garden of Shadows if you want background on the grandmother. Garden is probably my favorite in<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I would read Flowers, Petals On the Wind (revenge), and Garden of Shadows if you want background on the grandmother. Garden is probably my favorite in the series. You also learn more about the mother and how she was disowned by her mom and dad. I know this question was asked over a year ago, but I figure if anyone else is reading the q&amp;a, my post may be helpful,<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
